WEBVTT

01:25.700 --> 01:34.900
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.390 --> 01:37.870
[Episode 23]

01:43.670 --> 01:45.390
[Notice of participation
in the National Singer Competition]

01:47.180 --> 01:48.370
Right face!

01:48.840 --> 01:49.450
Rise!

01:49.580 --> 01:54.770
[Congratulations to Zhuang Zhuang for making it
to the finals of the Singer Competition]

01:54.810 --> 01:57.009
[Notice of participation
in the National Singer Competition]

01:57.110 --> 02:03.070
[Congratulations to Zhuang Zhuang for making it
to the finals of the Singer Competition]

02:05.330 --> 02:06.780
[Congratulations to Zhuang Zhuang for making it
to the finals of the Singer Competition]

02:09.750 --> 02:13.130
Welcome! Welcome!

02:13.310 --> 02:16.840
Welcome! Welcome!

02:16.840 --> 02:17.500
Have a seat!

02:19.650 --> 02:20.510
Zhuang Zhuang!

02:20.780 --> 02:22.710
Congratulations
on making it to the finals.

02:22.710 --> 02:23.579
All of us

02:23.840 --> 02:25.090
hope you achieve

02:25.310 --> 02:26.910
great results in the finals.

02:27.300 --> 02:30.820
Congratulations! Congratulations!

02:31.000 --> 02:34.340
Congratulations! Congratulations!

02:34.500 --> 02:35.210
Zhuang Zhuang

02:35.210 --> 02:36.360
will definitely win first place

02:36.360 --> 02:37.579
and become the champion.

02:37.579 --> 02:40.820
Zhuang Zhuang is the champion!

02:40.960 --> 02:44.290
Zhuang Zhuang is the champion!

02:44.579 --> 02:45.030
We were planning

02:45.030 --> 02:46.420
to eat out,

02:46.579 --> 02:47.310
but everyone felt

02:47.310 --> 02:49.370
it was better to stay in—
more comfortable.

02:49.370 --> 02:49.780
Yes.

02:50.079 --> 02:51.380
If we get drunk,

02:51.410 --> 02:53.070
we can just go to bed and sleep.

02:53.180 --> 02:53.620
Right?

02:53.650 --> 02:54.360
Xu said

02:54.410 --> 02:55.680
this meal today

02:55.800 --> 02:56.810
should show our sincerity,

02:56.810 --> 02:58.510
so each of us cooked a dish

02:58.650 --> 02:59.850
to make a full spread.

03:00.840 --> 03:03.100
Zhuang, we also prepared a performance.

03:03.690 --> 03:05.250
Cao prepared the performance.

03:05.250 --> 03:06.160
Introduce it.

03:06.430 --> 03:09.310
Zhuang Zhuang,
the fact that you made it to the finals

03:09.310 --> 03:10.440
really inspired us.

03:10.580 --> 03:11.000
You are

03:11.000 --> 03:12.300
the pride of our Seasons Change Hostel.

03:12.300 --> 03:12.960
You've warmed us

03:12.960 --> 03:13.890
and inspired us.

03:13.960 --> 03:15.210
You're not alone in this competition.

03:15.210 --> 03:16.520
You carry our dreams too.

03:16.520 --> 03:18.910
Yes, we all have to shine.

03:21.180 --> 03:24.120
Ready—

03:26.740 --> 03:29.620
Seven-character poem: The Long March.

03:30.340 --> 03:33.530
The Red Army fears not the Long March.

03:34.130 --> 03:37.280
Countless rivers and mountains
are but trivial.

03:38.020 --> 03:42.060
The Five Ridges rise in gentle waves.

03:42.579 --> 03:46.740
The grandeur of the Wumeng Mountains is nothing
more than clay balls rolling beneath our feet.

03:46.740 --> 03:49.840
The Jinsha River
warms the cliffs with splashes.

03:50.210 --> 03:54.310
The Dadu Bridge
chills with its iron chains.

03:54.620 --> 03:58.400
We rejoice in the snow
across the Min Mountains.

03:58.840 --> 04:03.180
After the three armies have crossed,
everyone's faces are beaming.

04:10.180 --> 04:10.840
Why are you crying?

04:10.840 --> 04:11.660
Look at you.

04:12.020 --> 04:13.020
What are you doing?

04:13.020 --> 04:13.880
Sit, sit.

04:14.530 --> 04:15.240
Sit.

04:15.370 --> 04:17.070
Come on, let's drink.

04:17.810 --> 04:19.010
Eat up.

04:19.100 --> 04:19.950
That was too much, wasn't it?

04:19.950 --> 04:20.410
Come on.

04:20.430 --> 04:21.829
Well, we wanted to make her happy.

04:21.829 --> 04:22.800
-Come on.
-To make her happy.

04:22.800 --> 04:23.930
She is. She is happy.

04:23.930 --> 04:24.600
Tears of joy.

04:24.600 --> 04:25.060
Come on.

04:27.810 --> 04:29.010
Come on, let's drink.

04:29.370 --> 04:31.300
Why do you need so much money again?

04:31.430 --> 04:33.230
Didn't I just transfer it to you?

04:34.770 --> 04:36.970
You know so many bosses.

04:37.070 --> 04:38.710
You can borrow from them.

04:39.390 --> 04:40.890
What bosses do I know?

04:42.330 --> 04:44.390
The one who came to our house last time.

04:44.390 --> 04:45.800
He's been to our home.

04:45.800 --> 04:47.670
Why can't you borrow from him?

04:47.830 --> 04:49.159
Come on. What does his richness

04:49.159 --> 04:50.330
have to do with me?

04:50.390 --> 04:51.130
Besides, why is Fufu

04:51.130 --> 04:52.960
in such a hurry to get married?

04:53.100 --> 04:55.590
But we need to prepare in advance.

04:56.000 --> 04:58.380
I'm living in a basement, Mom.

05:00.220 --> 05:01.670
What do you mean, Ranran?

05:01.830 --> 05:02.360
Do you

05:02.370 --> 05:04.030
not want to help your brother?

05:04.630 --> 05:06.100
Let me make it clear.

05:06.220 --> 05:07.480
All our family's money

05:07.500 --> 05:09.360
was spent on your acting classes.

05:09.360 --> 05:11.540
You have to contribute to the family.

05:11.870 --> 05:13.370
If you feel awkward

05:13.370 --> 05:14.690
borrowing money from those bosses,

05:14.690 --> 05:15.950
I can call

05:15.980 --> 05:16.840
Mr. Chu myself.

05:16.980 --> 05:17.950
Please don't.

05:19.930 --> 05:21.460
I got it. I'll figure it out.

05:21.500 --> 05:23.060
Okay, I'll wait for you.

05:33.050 --> 05:34.940
[Seasons Change Hostel]

05:40.220 --> 05:41.659
Zongbao, what are you doing?

05:41.659 --> 05:43.110
I finally got some sleep.

05:48.270 --> 05:49.870
Zongbao, what are you doing?

05:49.870 --> 05:50.870
I finally got to catch up on sleep,

05:50.870 --> 05:52.409
and you're doing renovations here?

05:52.409 --> 05:53.730
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

05:54.000 --> 05:55.720
I got a new gadget here.

05:55.800 --> 05:56.830
I was just trying it out.

05:56.830 --> 05:58.120
Come on. You...

05:58.390 --> 05:59.600
Not only are you mashing garlic here,

05:59.600 --> 06:00.740
you're also making a sound
like a power drill.

06:00.740 --> 06:01.800
What are you trying to do?

06:01.800 --> 06:02.460
I really...

06:02.560 --> 06:03.020
Come on.

06:03.770 --> 06:05.510
The garlic mashed by hand

06:03.810 --> 06:09.100
[Endeavor]

06:05.930 --> 06:07.450
tastes different from the garlic paste

06:07.450 --> 06:08.560
made by a machine.

06:09.830 --> 06:10.600
How is it different?

06:10.600 --> 06:11.660
What is that thing?

06:11.730 --> 06:14.670
[Endeavor]

06:12.130 --> 06:14.430
This is a juicer.

06:14.720 --> 06:15.360
Sir, sir.

06:15.480 --> 06:15.810
What?

06:15.830 --> 06:16.290
Well...

06:16.510 --> 06:17.600
You worked hard on the performance.

06:17.600 --> 06:19.060
Let's eat and drink together.

06:19.060 --> 06:19.620
I shouldn't.

06:19.620 --> 06:21.450
I have a performance, so I can't drink.

06:21.450 --> 06:22.680
Don't just drink water.

06:22.680 --> 06:24.080
Here, try this beverage.

06:24.120 --> 06:25.360
It's yam juice produced

06:25.360 --> 06:26.000
in our village.

06:26.000 --> 06:26.660
Have a taste.

06:26.660 --> 06:28.060
Have a taste and see how it is.

06:28.060 --> 06:30.270
You can make juice out of yams?

06:30.330 --> 06:32.290
Yes, it's very nutritious.

06:32.800 --> 06:33.400
Is that so?

06:35.240 --> 06:36.370
Refreshing, right?

06:36.720 --> 06:37.920
And it's low in sugar.

06:38.190 --> 06:38.950
It's quite sweet.

06:38.950 --> 06:40.270
Take some more.

06:40.750 --> 06:42.370
Try this.

06:44.310 --> 06:44.740
Here.

06:45.870 --> 06:46.730
Corn porridge?

06:47.420 --> 06:49.350
Corn juice. It's a drink.

06:49.420 --> 06:50.770
Come on. Try it.

06:53.070 --> 06:53.600
How is it?

06:54.420 --> 06:55.880
Isn't this corn porridge?

06:56.159 --> 06:57.040
Corn juice!

06:57.070 --> 06:58.570
It's a drink! A drink!

07:00.000 --> 07:01.430
Okay. It's a drink.

07:03.120 --> 07:03.860
Seriously.

07:04.680 --> 07:06.080
You are quite something.

07:06.300 --> 07:07.760
You kept researching here

07:07.830 --> 07:09.270
and came up with corn juice.

07:09.270 --> 07:10.450
This is nothing.

07:12.120 --> 07:14.020
It's just that, at home,

07:14.370 --> 07:16.800
we harvest so much corn every year.

07:17.360 --> 07:18.370
I was thinking,

07:18.830 --> 07:20.500
if we can't sell them

07:20.560 --> 07:22.150
or eat them all,

07:22.220 --> 07:23.360
isn't it a waste?

07:23.870 --> 07:24.810
It's a pity.

07:25.830 --> 07:26.920
While my wife

07:27.000 --> 07:29.370
is waiting in line for her surgery,

07:30.040 --> 07:31.700
I'll do some research on this.

07:32.220 --> 07:34.040
If yam juice can work,

07:34.130 --> 07:34.830
I believe

07:34.860 --> 07:35.980
my corn juice

07:36.680 --> 07:38.500
can shine too.

07:39.830 --> 07:40.630
That's great.

07:42.070 --> 07:43.930
Zongbao, keep researching this.

07:44.330 --> 07:45.720
I've had no idea what to eat

07:45.720 --> 07:47.330
these days anyway.

07:47.870 --> 07:48.570
Eat corn.

07:48.720 --> 07:49.240
Right.

07:49.750 --> 07:51.010
You focus on the juice,

07:51.070 --> 07:52.330
and I focus on the food.

07:53.560 --> 07:54.360
This is great.

07:54.480 --> 07:56.570
See? I don't even need to chew.

07:58.250 --> 07:58.680
What?

07:59.690 --> 08:01.370
Spit it out! Hurry!

08:03.060 --> 08:03.920
I swallowed it.

08:05.100 --> 08:06.270
Spit it out!

08:07.120 --> 08:08.450
I swallowed it already.

08:10.160 --> 08:13.710
This is what's left after I chewed it.

08:16.810 --> 08:19.140
You're not just keeping me from sleeping,

08:19.490 --> 08:20.990
you're trying to kill me.

08:24.480 --> 08:25.110
It's fine.

08:25.180 --> 08:26.280
It's very clean.

08:27.360 --> 08:29.310
You're always climbing up and down.

08:29.310 --> 08:30.510
What are you looking for? Let me help you.

08:30.510 --> 08:31.770
Come. Come down first.

08:32.630 --> 08:33.820
Found it.

08:34.580 --> 08:35.380
Give me a hand.

08:41.299 --> 08:42.490
[The Late Love]

08:41.700 --> 08:44.230
Do you still recognize
your own handwriting?

08:45.050 --> 08:47.450
I'd recognize it
even if it turned to ashes.

08:48.530 --> 08:49.510
Did you call me over today

08:49.510 --> 08:50.980
because of The Late Love?

08:51.840 --> 08:53.700
I told that stubborn mule long ago

08:54.150 --> 08:55.770
that the title wasn't good luck.

08:55.770 --> 08:57.000
The Late Love?

08:57.030 --> 08:58.430
He just wouldn't listen.

08:58.580 --> 08:59.620
Director,

08:59.650 --> 09:01.240
you always keep me guessing.

09:01.240 --> 09:02.940
Can you just be frank?

09:03.500 --> 09:06.390
The Late Love
is finally seeing a breakthrough.

09:08.670 --> 09:09.890
The studio agreed to make it?

09:09.890 --> 09:10.780
Not really.

09:11.390 --> 09:12.820
Your master won't change a single word.

09:12.820 --> 09:14.020
Why would they agree?

09:14.250 --> 09:15.890
Then what happened?

09:16.790 --> 09:18.520
A film studio from another city

09:18.870 --> 09:20.600
received the script you sent in

09:20.620 --> 09:22.150
and thought it was very good.

09:22.150 --> 09:24.080
Of course, they do have some notes,

09:24.290 --> 09:26.540
but overall they're positive about it.

09:26.960 --> 09:28.840
A studio from another city?

09:28.970 --> 09:30.670
I never sent it out.

09:31.170 --> 09:32.710
Then someone must have

09:33.080 --> 09:34.700
done it for you.

09:41.010 --> 09:42.140
It's Zhuang Zhuang.

09:52.080 --> 09:55.050
My girlfriend is the best in the world!

09:57.890 --> 09:58.950
What are you doing?

09:59.130 --> 10:00.860
Someone has picked our script!

10:01.460 --> 10:02.380
Really?

10:03.700 --> 10:04.920
That's great!

10:05.010 --> 10:05.810
That's great!

10:07.010 --> 10:07.890
That's great!

10:09.390 --> 10:09.990
Thank you.

10:13.010 --> 10:13.500
I...

10:14.250 --> 10:15.870
I just felt the script was so good

10:15.870 --> 10:17.330
and shouldn't go to waste.

10:40.320 --> 10:41.510
Pick up your bag.

10:51.700 --> 10:52.560
Thank me again.

10:55.750 --> 10:58.200
Then... then I want to kiss you again.

11:02.340 --> 11:03.730
We're on the street.

11:05.250 --> 11:05.780
Alright.

11:06.600 --> 11:07.390
From now on,

11:07.390 --> 11:08.200
if you miss me,

11:08.220 --> 11:09.550
you can page me anytime.

11:10.220 --> 11:11.080
Who'd miss you?

11:12.510 --> 11:13.490
Who'd miss me?

11:13.740 --> 11:14.530
You waited for me until this late,

11:14.530 --> 11:15.730
and you don't miss me?

11:16.520 --> 11:19.210
[Capital Film Studio]

11:16.960 --> 11:19.040
I called you here to tell you

11:19.250 --> 11:20.650
that the film studio said

11:20.800 --> 11:22.270
that with such a good script,

11:22.270 --> 11:24.600
they would invest a little no matter what.

11:24.750 --> 11:26.050
However,

11:27.530 --> 11:28.870
we still have to cover

11:29.100 --> 11:31.130
the bulk of the funding ourselves.

11:31.480 --> 11:32.610
Ourselves?

11:34.080 --> 11:34.620
You know,

11:34.650 --> 11:36.320
everything's market-driven now.

11:36.320 --> 11:38.200
Things aren't easy at the studio either.

11:38.200 --> 11:40.260
How about this? Let's try all the ways

11:40.630 --> 11:42.840
and see if any

11:42.960 --> 11:44.380
private film companies

11:44.630 --> 11:45.130
or

11:45.150 --> 11:46.720
businessmen from other industries

11:46.720 --> 11:47.980
are willing to invest.

11:49.720 --> 11:50.390
But Director Weng,

11:50.390 --> 11:52.050
I don't have any connections.

11:54.290 --> 11:55.500
Each film has its own destiny.

11:55.500 --> 11:56.500
Take it as it comes

11:56.500 --> 11:57.430
and try our luck.

11:57.650 --> 11:59.180
I'll also try to ask around.

12:02.870 --> 12:03.960
Here is the situation.

12:03.960 --> 12:04.690
Well...

12:04.740 --> 12:07.150
the patient we had scheduled

12:07.250 --> 12:09.390
has a heart problem
found in pre-op checks,

12:09.390 --> 12:10.870
so the surgery can't be done.

12:10.870 --> 12:12.370
From the registrations,

12:12.700 --> 12:13.460
the best candidate now

12:13.460 --> 12:15.060
is your wife, Jiang Hongmei.

12:15.960 --> 12:18.270
She has post-lingual deafness,

12:18.370 --> 12:20.530
with relatively intact cochlear structure,

12:20.530 --> 12:21.700
making her the ideal candidate.

12:21.700 --> 12:22.770
If we delay

12:22.770 --> 12:23.460
too long,

12:23.460 --> 12:25.080
the surgery's effectiveness will decrease.

12:25.080 --> 12:26.620
Okay, that's great.

12:27.080 --> 12:28.820
Of course, this is a rare opportunity.

12:28.820 --> 12:30.460
If you decide to go ahead
with the surgery,

12:30.460 --> 12:32.390
get the patient admitted quickly.

12:33.650 --> 12:34.370
Great.

12:34.980 --> 12:36.840
My wife...

12:37.860 --> 12:39.050
is really lucky.

12:39.620 --> 12:41.510
But if she's admitted immediately,

12:41.510 --> 12:43.410
we need to pay right away, right?

12:43.890 --> 12:45.130
If you decide to do it,

12:45.170 --> 12:45.890
yes.

12:46.630 --> 12:47.890
As I told you last time,

12:48.050 --> 12:50.200
this is entirely self-funded—

12:50.350 --> 12:51.950
surgery, cochlear implant,

12:52.050 --> 12:53.240
and post-op rehab—

12:54.720 --> 12:55.390
financially,

12:55.390 --> 12:57.050
you need to be fully prepared.

12:57.670 --> 12:59.580
But can we delay it a bit?

13:00.170 --> 13:02.230
I haven't gathered enough money yet.

13:02.360 --> 13:03.940
Can I pay part of it first?

13:03.980 --> 13:04.840
Will that work?

13:05.670 --> 13:07.600
Then you'll have to queue up again.

13:07.750 --> 13:08.270
If

13:08.270 --> 13:10.220
more eligible patients come after,

13:10.220 --> 13:12.150
I can't say when it'll be your turn.

13:12.170 --> 13:12.770
I know.

13:13.890 --> 13:14.490
Of course,

13:14.700 --> 13:15.960
a surgery like this

13:15.960 --> 13:17.010
is indeed a heavy burden

13:17.010 --> 13:18.240
for a normal family,

13:18.820 --> 13:20.700
so you must think it through.

13:20.790 --> 13:21.450
Don't rush.

13:22.360 --> 13:23.300
We'll also

13:23.460 --> 13:24.120
get in touch

13:24.170 --> 13:26.010
with the next suitable patient.

13:26.290 --> 13:27.980
You can't do that.

13:28.750 --> 13:29.880
Don't contact them.

13:30.130 --> 13:31.910
I'll go borrow the money.

13:32.960 --> 13:35.790
It wasn't easy for my wife

13:35.820 --> 13:37.670
to wait for this surgery.

13:37.980 --> 13:39.290
I'll go borrow money.

13:40.290 --> 13:41.820
Can you wait a few more days?

13:44.220 --> 13:44.740
Alright.

13:44.740 --> 13:46.340
I'll let the department know

13:46.700 --> 13:47.580
and give you a few days.

13:47.580 --> 13:48.350
Okay.

13:48.460 --> 13:50.080
Thank you, then.

13:50.390 --> 13:51.100
-It's alright.
-Thank you.

13:51.100 --> 13:52.240
It's alright.

13:53.030 --> 13:54.230
I'll get going then.

13:54.340 --> 13:54.750
Okay.

13:55.620 --> 13:56.460
Hurry up then.

13:56.870 --> 13:57.580
Okay.

14:03.080 --> 14:04.580
Here's 820.

14:05.320 --> 14:07.130
I'll write you an IOU.

14:09.120 --> 14:10.130
No need. No need.

14:10.130 --> 14:11.340
There's no need for that.

14:11.340 --> 14:14.070
Come on. Even brothers
settle accounts clearly.

14:15.340 --> 14:17.160
I paid the tuition for my eldest
before the new year,

14:17.160 --> 14:18.890
so I only have this little bit left.

14:18.890 --> 14:20.500
Otherwise, I could give you more.

14:20.500 --> 14:21.240
Just use it for now.

14:21.240 --> 14:22.840
Why write an IOU?

14:22.420 --> 14:24.600
[I borrowed 820 yuan from Wang Qing today]

14:22.980 --> 14:23.840
We've known each other for so many years.

14:23.840 --> 14:25.040
If the villagers know

14:25.100 --> 14:25.960
that you wrote me an IOU,

14:25.960 --> 14:27.490
what would they think of us?

14:28.150 --> 14:28.790
Then write it.

14:28.790 --> 14:30.320
I'll just tear it up anyway.

14:30.510 --> 14:31.850
Stop messing around.

14:32.170 --> 14:32.570
You...

14:32.600 --> 14:33.630
Just take it.

14:33.630 --> 14:35.560
If you give it to me, I'll tear it up.

14:36.320 --> 14:37.580
I'll tear it up anyway.

14:37.870 --> 14:38.750
Take it.

14:38.750 --> 14:39.370
Don't give it to me.

14:39.370 --> 14:39.770
You...

14:40.630 --> 14:42.820
Zongbao, let me say a few more words.

14:43.480 --> 14:44.670
Don't get mad, okay?

14:45.410 --> 14:45.860
What?

14:48.870 --> 14:50.800
We all know you're good to Hongmei.

14:51.270 --> 14:52.530
But some things are...

14:52.940 --> 14:55.080
are just out of our reach.

14:56.080 --> 14:56.720
We have to consider

14:56.720 --> 14:58.710
our own conditions.

15:03.320 --> 15:04.010
Thanks.

15:04.980 --> 15:07.050
I will definitely pay you back.

15:07.890 --> 15:08.290
You...

15:08.360 --> 15:08.960
Take it.

15:16.720 --> 15:17.450
I'm leaving.

15:17.740 --> 15:18.590
Take care.

15:18.740 --> 15:19.410
Thanks.

15:22.840 --> 15:26.940
Repairing range hoods!

15:28.200 --> 15:31.010
Unclogging drains!

15:33.290 --> 15:37.130
Sharpening scissors

15:38.790 --> 15:42.740
and knives!

15:44.650 --> 15:45.340
Shengli, you're here.

15:45.340 --> 15:45.940
Zongbao.

15:46.740 --> 15:48.270
Here, your letter. Take it.

15:49.200 --> 15:49.930
What letter?

15:51.480 --> 15:52.360
Wait, this...

15:53.460 --> 15:54.630
This is money!

15:55.620 --> 15:56.500
This is just a little something

15:56.500 --> 15:57.620
from me and Zhuang Zhuang.

15:57.620 --> 15:58.600
Please take it.

15:59.320 --> 15:59.910
Come on.

16:01.050 --> 16:02.340
I can't accept this money.

16:02.340 --> 16:03.870
It's not easy for you to make money.

16:03.870 --> 16:04.320
Don't!

16:04.320 --> 16:05.820
You're not planning to pay it back,

16:05.820 --> 16:06.320
are you?

16:06.550 --> 16:08.010
We are lending this to you.

16:08.220 --> 16:08.750
Lending?

16:11.290 --> 16:11.750
Well...

16:12.980 --> 16:13.960
Thank you, then.

16:15.030 --> 16:16.030
I'll write you...

16:16.100 --> 16:17.410
an IOU.

16:18.360 --> 16:18.840
Okay.

16:18.890 --> 16:19.580
Sure.

16:19.720 --> 16:20.550
Okay.

16:25.410 --> 16:25.810
You...

16:26.550 --> 16:27.530
Well, I...

16:28.740 --> 16:29.600
Shengli!

17:09.640 --> 17:10.089
Cao.

17:12.030 --> 17:13.130
What is this?

17:13.250 --> 17:13.780
Zongbao.

17:15.089 --> 17:16.099
About Mrs. Jiang,

17:16.230 --> 17:17.760
I've always wanted to help,

17:18.220 --> 17:19.619
but my means are limited.

17:19.829 --> 17:20.960
Anyway, just let me chip in.

17:20.960 --> 17:22.619
Please don't mind the amount.

17:23.960 --> 17:25.849
I'll write you an IOU.

17:25.940 --> 17:27.000
Come on, drop it.

17:27.030 --> 17:28.700
Stop talking. If you say more...

17:28.700 --> 17:29.630
I'm going to cry.

17:31.420 --> 17:32.150
Cao, you...

17:36.250 --> 17:37.290
Liang, you're back?

17:37.290 --> 17:37.880
Zongbao.

17:42.110 --> 17:43.270
This is all the ca-

17:43.350 --> 17:44.130
cash I have.

17:44.750 --> 17:46.410
It's just a token of my regard.

17:46.880 --> 17:47.480
Come on...

17:47.680 --> 17:49.140
Don't worry about it.

18:10.050 --> 18:10.580
Who is it?

18:13.720 --> 18:14.180
Mr. Guo?

18:18.350 --> 18:19.050
Ranran.

18:19.290 --> 18:20.290
Why are you here?

18:20.530 --> 18:22.090
No-nothing.

18:22.110 --> 18:24.490
I... I just need some fresh air.

18:24.830 --> 18:26.030
And you're drinking?

18:28.030 --> 18:29.080
Well, have...

18:29.180 --> 18:29.960
have a seat.

18:35.850 --> 18:37.980
Do you have something on your mind too?

18:38.940 --> 18:39.600
Have a seat.

18:52.380 --> 18:52.980
What's...

18:54.250 --> 18:55.610
bothering you?

18:55.790 --> 18:56.680
Tell me.

18:58.070 --> 19:00.160
Let me cheer you up.

19:05.250 --> 19:07.350
I came up to see the m—

19:09.940 --> 19:10.600
The moon...

19:11.720 --> 19:12.320
Here it is.

19:12.570 --> 19:14.340
It ran over there. Look.

19:16.230 --> 19:17.420
The moon today

19:17.610 --> 19:18.180
is so big

19:19.250 --> 19:20.050
and so bright.

19:21.810 --> 19:22.610
It's awesome.

19:24.180 --> 19:25.500
Seeing this moon

19:26.380 --> 19:29.940
reminds me of my wife and I.

19:31.810 --> 19:33.270
The night we got married,

19:33.980 --> 19:36.490
the moon was this big.

19:37.400 --> 19:38.260
It was amazing.

19:39.140 --> 19:40.340
I told her...

19:41.460 --> 19:42.240
I said,

19:43.160 --> 19:46.200
"Let's live a good life,

19:47.750 --> 19:49.150
and I'll take care of you.

19:52.070 --> 19:54.000
Even if you want the moon in the sky,

19:55.740 --> 19:57.090
I'll get it for you."

20:07.050 --> 20:08.440
When I was little,

20:09.510 --> 20:10.740
I also clamored every day

20:10.740 --> 20:12.470
for my dad to get the moon for me.

20:13.010 --> 20:13.980
Guess what?

20:14.940 --> 20:16.300
My dad placed

20:16.400 --> 20:18.260
a big basin of water in front of me.

20:18.380 --> 20:19.850
He said, "Look,

20:20.500 --> 20:20.980
isn't the moon

20:20.980 --> 20:22.110
right in the basin?"

20:24.380 --> 20:27.320
Then I tried to grab it,

20:27.590 --> 20:28.940
but caught nothing.

20:29.500 --> 20:30.350
I told my dad,

20:31.070 --> 20:33.010
"Dad, you're a big liar.

20:33.250 --> 20:34.110
You lied to me."

20:35.460 --> 20:37.330
Your dad wasn't lying.

20:38.480 --> 20:40.180
At that time, your dad

20:40.270 --> 20:42.330
really wanted to get the moon for you.

20:42.940 --> 20:44.220
Fathers

20:44.830 --> 20:46.030
love their daughters

20:46.240 --> 20:47.740
so much.

20:51.980 --> 20:53.360
Your dad was smart.

20:54.640 --> 20:57.410
If my wife asked me for the moon,

20:57.570 --> 20:59.400
I wouldn't think of that trick.

21:06.450 --> 21:07.250
What's wrong?

21:08.480 --> 21:09.270
I miss my dad.

21:20.830 --> 21:21.640
It's so round.

21:24.920 --> 21:26.180
Mr. Guo, what's wrong?

21:27.010 --> 21:28.220
My wife and I...

21:31.020 --> 21:33.240
grew up together.

21:33.510 --> 21:34.680
In this life,

21:35.330 --> 21:36.630
I just want her

21:37.510 --> 21:39.310
to hear the birds singing again,

21:40.610 --> 21:42.140
hear me speak again,

21:43.920 --> 21:45.060
and hear me

21:45.500 --> 21:47.230
sing Henan opera for her again.

21:53.180 --> 21:53.840
Mr. Guo,

21:55.270 --> 21:57.070
haven't you saved enough money?

21:58.200 --> 21:58.750
They say

21:58.750 --> 22:01.830
a penny can stump a hero.

22:03.720 --> 22:05.110
I'm still short 60,000.

22:07.790 --> 22:09.120
I haven't saved enough,

22:10.070 --> 22:12.800
but the opportunity for the surgery
has arrived.

22:13.200 --> 22:14.090
Right now,

22:15.140 --> 22:16.350
I'm restless

22:17.530 --> 22:19.270
and don't know what to do.

22:23.440 --> 22:26.660
Mr. Guo, things will work out eventually.

22:27.790 --> 22:29.790
Eventually?

22:31.180 --> 22:34.900
The "eventually" is next week.

22:36.140 --> 22:37.610
But where is the way out?

22:38.590 --> 22:40.140
Where is the money?

22:40.830 --> 22:42.530
Let's bring her to Beijing

22:42.940 --> 22:44.800
and have her undergo the surgery.

22:46.850 --> 22:47.780
What did you say?

22:51.350 --> 22:52.750
Don't leave. Wait for me.

22:53.240 --> 22:53.880
Ranran.

22:55.420 --> 22:57.020
What were you talking about?

23:06.640 --> 23:09.100
Why did I tell a kid about this?

23:33.810 --> 23:34.350
Ranran.

23:35.430 --> 23:37.560
Mr. Guo, here.

23:36.090 --> 23:37.470
[Passbook Savings Account]

23:37.700 --> 23:38.200
Take it.

23:41.050 --> 23:41.660
Take it.

23:41.540 --> 23:42.440
[Passbook Savings Account]

23:42.640 --> 23:45.140
What are you doing?

23:46.160 --> 23:47.290
This is my pay

23:47.850 --> 23:49.050
and the money I saved.

23:49.510 --> 23:50.640
It should be enough.

23:55.880 --> 23:56.400
Ranran.

23:58.590 --> 24:01.740
This favor is too heavy.

24:04.330 --> 24:06.700
I can't accept it.

24:07.110 --> 24:09.630
Curing her is more important, Mr. Guo.

24:13.550 --> 24:14.110
Alright.

24:16.350 --> 24:17.080
I'll take it.

24:19.810 --> 24:21.470
I'll definitely pay you back.

24:22.670 --> 24:24.870
I don't need to use this money right now.

24:26.000 --> 24:27.800
Let's get the moon for you first.

24:35.920 --> 24:36.660
Good girl.

24:52.530 --> 24:53.310
Good.

24:59.150 --> 24:59.790
Mr. Sui,

25:00.090 --> 25:02.460
did you read the script?

25:02.810 --> 25:03.940
Are you interested?

25:04.440 --> 25:05.030
I am.

25:06.330 --> 25:07.180
Great.

25:07.480 --> 25:08.880
Are we talking about art

25:09.440 --> 25:10.610
or business?

25:10.980 --> 25:12.810
Well... of course we...

25:13.660 --> 25:14.480
In business,

25:17.090 --> 25:18.440
spending money is making money.

25:18.440 --> 25:19.740
Exactly.

25:21.550 --> 25:22.140
Mr. Sui,

25:22.720 --> 25:24.590
since you want to be straightforward,

25:24.590 --> 25:25.890
let's speak frankly,

25:26.090 --> 25:26.720
okay?

25:26.880 --> 25:28.310
No movie

25:28.770 --> 25:30.550
would dare claim it's guaranteed

25:30.550 --> 25:32.210
to make money before release.

25:32.400 --> 25:34.110
But I can guarantee

25:34.440 --> 25:36.720
that the script is absolutely good.

25:37.400 --> 25:39.000
As long as the funds are in place,

25:39.000 --> 25:40.250
I can immediately gather

25:40.250 --> 25:41.260
the best actors

25:41.500 --> 25:43.070
and a good production team.

25:45.220 --> 25:46.080
Director Weng,

25:46.850 --> 25:48.250
your words

25:48.500 --> 25:49.180
make me feel

25:50.250 --> 25:52.380
that you are not only straightforward

25:52.550 --> 25:53.660
but also honest.

25:55.200 --> 25:56.610
If you patted your chest and said

25:56.610 --> 25:58.870
this movie would definitely make money,

25:58.940 --> 26:00.740
I would disappear immediately.

26:01.590 --> 26:03.030
In front of a straightforward person,

26:03.030 --> 26:04.350
I wouldn't dare not be straightforward,

26:04.350 --> 26:04.880
right?

26:05.140 --> 26:05.710
Right.

26:05.850 --> 26:07.310
I can invest in this movie.

26:08.270 --> 26:09.000
To me,

26:10.070 --> 26:11.010
it's pocket money.

26:11.010 --> 26:12.540
I can even fund it entirely.

26:12.880 --> 26:14.140
That's great, Mr. Sui.

26:14.500 --> 26:16.100
It took us a long time to write

26:16.160 --> 26:17.160
the script for this movie.

26:17.160 --> 26:17.560
Right.

26:17.700 --> 26:18.830
Director Weng and I
want to make this movie a success

26:18.830 --> 26:20.110
more than anyone else.

26:20.310 --> 26:21.530
Yes.

26:24.160 --> 26:26.330
You were introduced by Mr. Li?

26:26.400 --> 26:27.470
Yes.

26:28.200 --> 26:29.220
I mean...

26:30.160 --> 26:32.180
we take the risk together.

26:32.460 --> 26:33.680
You invest a portion too,

26:33.680 --> 26:35.010
and we can work together

26:35.090 --> 26:36.330
to make a good movie.

26:36.510 --> 26:36.980
Yes.

26:37.180 --> 26:38.180
Even if we lose,

26:38.180 --> 26:39.640
we still have the next one.

26:39.920 --> 26:40.500
Right?

26:41.180 --> 26:41.730
Look.

26:42.030 --> 26:43.900
If I'm the only one investing,

26:45.090 --> 26:46.220
I'll feel like

26:47.290 --> 26:49.510
you guys see me

26:49.700 --> 26:51.110
as some fool who doesn't know anything

26:51.110 --> 26:52.000
about the industry.

26:52.000 --> 26:52.330
No, no, no.

26:52.330 --> 26:53.900
Mr. Sui, you shouldn't think that way.

26:53.900 --> 26:55.020
We never thought that way.

26:55.020 --> 26:55.950
Absolutely not.

26:57.610 --> 26:58.670
Just kidding.

27:01.330 --> 27:02.990
Mr. Sui, how about this?

27:03.350 --> 27:04.660
Give us some time.

27:04.790 --> 27:06.090
We'll figure something out

27:06.090 --> 27:07.570
to show you our sincerity,

27:07.680 --> 27:08.220
okay?

27:08.550 --> 27:11.830
Good, it's the thought that counts.

27:12.530 --> 27:14.130
It's actually quite simple.

27:14.500 --> 27:16.330
You can just get a bank loan.

27:17.240 --> 27:19.310
Individuals and businesses

27:19.330 --> 27:20.330
can all get loans.

27:20.810 --> 27:22.220
As long as you have collateral.

27:22.220 --> 27:23.400
The procedures are very simple.

27:23.400 --> 27:25.240
The interest rate is also very reasonable.

27:25.240 --> 27:25.770
However,

27:26.460 --> 27:27.070
there's one thing

27:27.070 --> 27:28.530
you might not like to hear.

27:28.590 --> 27:30.140
Since I'm investing the bulk of it,

27:30.140 --> 27:31.380
the loan you get from the bank

27:31.380 --> 27:33.110
needs to be transferred
to my company's account.

27:33.110 --> 27:34.840
It's easier to manage that way.

27:35.090 --> 27:37.220
I really don't know anything
about making movies.

27:37.220 --> 27:37.720
See?

27:38.160 --> 27:40.000
This golf course is mine.

27:40.850 --> 27:41.270
When the time comes,

27:41.270 --> 27:42.460
if you need to use this venue or whatever,

27:42.460 --> 27:43.640
there will be no location fee.

27:43.640 --> 27:44.810
Film whatever you want.

27:44.810 --> 27:45.740
You can use the money

27:45.740 --> 27:46.590
however you want.

27:46.590 --> 27:47.920
I'll fully support you.

27:48.700 --> 27:49.630
Just one thing—

27:49.830 --> 27:51.160
what I need is not money,

27:51.400 --> 27:54.290
but sincerity and confidence.

27:55.290 --> 27:55.940
In short,

27:56.680 --> 27:57.530
integrity.

27:59.510 --> 28:01.510
Alright, I'll take a few more putts.

28:01.590 --> 28:02.250
Okay, okay.

28:02.310 --> 28:02.970
Okay, okay.

28:12.660 --> 28:13.520
Director Weng.

28:14.270 --> 28:15.870
I really want to give it a try.

28:17.160 --> 28:20.700
You decided to get a personal loan?

28:22.850 --> 28:23.400
Well...

28:24.180 --> 28:25.330
Hasn't Mr. Sui

28:25.350 --> 28:25.900
been friends with your friend

28:25.900 --> 28:27.210
for many years?

28:27.380 --> 28:29.030
He's invested in movies before.

28:29.030 --> 28:30.400
Didn't he also say that...

28:30.400 --> 28:31.250
that golf course

28:31.250 --> 28:32.010
was his?

28:32.610 --> 28:34.270
I think he's pretty reliable.

28:34.440 --> 28:35.220
He also said

28:35.440 --> 28:36.820
he'll put up 60%.

28:37.200 --> 28:38.800
The studio will put up a part,

28:38.880 --> 28:40.680
and we'll work hard for the rest.

28:40.960 --> 28:42.960
If we miss an opportunity like this,

28:43.070 --> 28:44.870
it'll be hard to get another one.

28:45.810 --> 28:46.200
Yeah.

28:47.900 --> 28:50.030
But do you have any assets to mortgage?

28:53.680 --> 28:54.420
N-No.

28:57.250 --> 28:57.780
Alright.

28:58.530 --> 29:00.720
I really appreciate you as a person,

29:01.010 --> 29:02.940
and I also really like this script.

29:04.400 --> 29:06.060
This isn't the first time

29:06.090 --> 29:07.010
I've worked on a film

29:07.010 --> 29:08.010
with your master.

29:08.010 --> 29:09.360
But this time

29:10.380 --> 29:11.160
it means something very different

29:11.160 --> 29:13.840
for both of you.

29:13.960 --> 29:16.580
I've also put a lot of effort
into polishing it,

29:16.660 --> 29:19.050
and the work has sparked something
completely new.

29:19.050 --> 29:20.580
This is the work of all of us.

29:20.660 --> 29:22.510
Since it's our joint effort,

29:23.250 --> 29:24.510
we'll share any risks

29:24.510 --> 29:25.440
together.

29:26.270 --> 29:27.000
I

29:27.400 --> 29:28.460
have an apartment.

29:28.740 --> 29:29.960
I'll use it as collateral for you.

29:29.960 --> 29:30.510
Okay!

29:31.270 --> 29:32.770
I'll go apply for the loan tomorrow!

29:32.770 --> 29:33.230
Come on!

29:43.530 --> 29:45.590
I'm sure this movie will be a success.

29:45.850 --> 29:48.140
That spirit of fighting for your dreams

29:48.180 --> 29:49.810
with all your might in the movie

29:49.810 --> 29:51.110
really hit me.

29:51.250 --> 29:52.960
Just thinking about directing this work

29:52.960 --> 29:54.250
makes me very excited.

29:55.180 --> 29:56.740
Of course, once filming starts,

29:56.740 --> 29:58.870
we'll face all sorts of difficulties.

29:59.330 --> 30:01.030
During the preparation phase,

30:01.030 --> 30:02.220
you'll worry

30:02.330 --> 30:03.530
if shooting can start smoothly.

30:03.530 --> 30:05.460
Once filming begins, you'll worry

30:05.570 --> 30:08.090
if it can finish on schedule.

30:08.250 --> 30:09.380
After the shoot wraps, you'll wonder

30:09.380 --> 30:10.680
if the movie will be released
successfully.

30:10.680 --> 30:11.940
And once it's out, you'll worry about

30:11.940 --> 30:12.770
whether it will lose money

30:12.770 --> 30:13.930
or face criticism.

30:14.140 --> 30:16.030
But none of that

30:16.590 --> 30:17.720
can dampen

30:18.030 --> 30:19.960
the excitement you feel right now.

30:22.180 --> 30:22.580
Right!

30:24.440 --> 30:25.460
Are you laughing at me?

30:25.460 --> 30:26.140
Are you making fun of me?

30:26.140 --> 30:27.420
No, I'm not.

30:28.000 --> 30:28.500
It's just that...

30:28.500 --> 30:29.660
listening to you speak just now,

30:29.660 --> 30:30.790
I suddenly felt like

30:31.240 --> 30:32.400
we're…

30:32.790 --> 30:34.120
like we're the same age.

30:35.420 --> 30:36.740
That's why

30:36.790 --> 30:38.490
I like making movies.

30:38.940 --> 30:41.220
It's about the warmth
and coldness of people,

30:41.220 --> 30:43.420
the joy, anger, sorrow, and happiness.

30:43.460 --> 30:45.010
Once I get the loan,

30:45.090 --> 30:46.150
I'll tell my master

30:46.330 --> 30:47.140
about this.

30:47.920 --> 30:50.220
No, don't tell him.

30:50.400 --> 30:51.640
We'll wait until shooting starts

30:51.640 --> 30:53.180
and give him a surprise.

30:53.810 --> 30:55.260
We'll trick him into coming over

30:55.260 --> 30:56.880
and shock him big time.

30:57.920 --> 30:58.450
Alright!

31:01.380 --> 31:02.240
Director Weng.

31:03.880 --> 31:04.940
Is our movie

31:06.700 --> 31:08.500
really going to start shooting?

31:08.550 --> 31:09.990
Isn't it too dramatic?

31:12.330 --> 31:13.100
So,

31:13.720 --> 31:14.960
things in this world

31:15.820 --> 31:17.190
are far more exciting

31:17.220 --> 31:18.440
than any movie.

31:19.000 --> 31:20.000
Ups and downs

31:20.460 --> 31:23.050
can happen overnight.

31:24.590 --> 31:25.050
Come on.

31:27.340 --> 31:31.320
[Peking Union Medical College Hospital]

31:50.590 --> 31:51.220
Well,

31:51.250 --> 31:52.940
doctor, let me say something.

31:56.110 --> 32:00.420
Don't worry.
Just treat it like going to sleep.

32:27.510 --> 32:28.310
You're awake?

32:30.330 --> 32:32.040
Um, the doctor...

32:32.070 --> 32:33.270
The doctor...

32:33.790 --> 32:34.590
said...

32:35.000 --> 32:37.140
He said that your cochlea

32:37.740 --> 32:39.590
will be functional

32:39.850 --> 32:40.810
in one month.

32:41.700 --> 32:42.850
In one month.

32:49.700 --> 32:51.050
Have some.

32:52.400 --> 32:53.330
A little closer.

33:02.240 --> 33:04.100
Are you really going to get a loan?

33:04.720 --> 33:05.680
Let me remind you.

33:05.680 --> 33:07.280
We're just ordinary people.

33:08.600 --> 33:10.580
There are risks involved in this.

33:09.710 --> 33:13.320
[Seasons Change Hostel]
[Inside the Yard]

33:12.220 --> 33:14.050
Well, for this script,

33:14.050 --> 33:15.980
we've been struggling for so long.

33:16.050 --> 33:17.500
Now the thing I've always wanted to do

33:17.500 --> 33:18.760
is right in front of me.

33:20.380 --> 33:21.240
If it were you,

33:21.250 --> 33:22.580
would you take a gamble?

33:23.900 --> 33:24.550
Me?

33:26.440 --> 33:27.710
I just feel like,

33:27.830 --> 33:28.720
back then,

33:29.740 --> 33:31.460
we treated our dreams
as the most important thing.

33:31.460 --> 33:32.770
But come to think of it now,

33:32.770 --> 33:34.600
we are nothing without money.

33:35.400 --> 33:36.460
And having no money

33:37.550 --> 33:38.240
and no dream

33:38.850 --> 33:39.940
is even worse.

33:41.290 --> 33:42.290
Something's off.

33:44.200 --> 33:45.730
Why are you so negative now?

33:46.530 --> 33:47.390
What happened?

33:48.290 --> 33:48.950
Nothing.

33:48.980 --> 33:49.940
Don't give me that.

33:49.940 --> 33:50.670
Just tell me.

33:54.290 --> 33:55.270
I just feel like

33:57.050 --> 33:59.180
I wasn't brave when I should have been,

33:59.940 --> 34:03.190
and I didn't make money
when I should have.

34:03.700 --> 34:05.030
Is it because of Ranran?

34:06.030 --> 34:07.770
If you two have any misunderstandings,

34:07.770 --> 34:09.080
can't you just

34:09.110 --> 34:10.210
explain it to her?

34:10.300 --> 34:11.510
There are no misunderstandings.

34:11.510 --> 34:12.760
What could I even explain?

34:12.760 --> 34:14.330
She's avoiding me now.

34:14.710 --> 34:15.790
Even if we meet,

34:15.820 --> 34:17.190
I wouldn't know what to say.

34:17.190 --> 34:18.820
That's her choice.

34:19.400 --> 34:20.730
You need to express what you want to say

34:20.730 --> 34:21.400
clearly.

34:21.480 --> 34:22.690
That's your business.

34:22.690 --> 34:23.650
It is my business.

34:23.650 --> 34:25.250
But what can I express to her?

34:25.400 --> 34:26.460
What can I give her?

34:27.030 --> 34:28.230
Didn't you wait until

34:28.230 --> 34:29.340
after you earned money in Russia

34:29.340 --> 34:31.260
before settling things with Zhuang Zhuang?

34:31.260 --> 34:32.730
That has nothing to do with money.

34:32.730 --> 34:34.090
How does it not?

34:34.130 --> 34:35.170
If you and Jun

34:35.210 --> 34:36.780
hadn't barged in that day,

34:36.940 --> 34:38.800
we would've settled things then.

34:42.110 --> 34:44.270
Fine. If you really think

34:44.300 --> 34:46.300
making money can solve the problem,

34:46.510 --> 34:47.630
then go earn it.

34:48.090 --> 34:50.280
Don't worry about
if you can actually make it.

34:50.280 --> 34:50.940
At least it's better

34:50.940 --> 34:53.070
than just sitting here overthinking.

34:56.590 --> 34:57.050
Come on.

34:57.780 --> 34:58.510
To you.

34:58.020 --> 35:06.050
[Seasons Change Hostel]
[Inside the Yard]

34:58.940 --> 34:59.360
Right?

35:00.940 --> 35:03.270
Sorry for interrupting your good moment.

35:05.090 --> 35:06.420
You still didn't get it.

35:08.840 --> 35:09.610
I did.

35:12.360 --> 35:14.160
I interrupted your good moment.

35:17.440 --> 35:18.550
Let me do a flip for you.

35:18.550 --> 35:20.570
I've been practicing side flips recently.

35:20.570 --> 35:22.500
-Look. I'll show you.
-Go ahead. Show me.

35:22.500 --> 35:23.000
Look.

35:24.810 --> 35:27.010
[Seasons Change Hostel]
[Inside the Yard]

35:25.940 --> 35:26.670
Not bad, huh?

35:27.890 --> 35:35.020
[Destined to Meet Co., Ltd.,]

35:28.730 --> 35:30.460
Right, they have 50

35:30.580 --> 35:32.730
JC 10 high-speed sewing machines.

35:33.570 --> 35:34.860
It's a sewing machine,

35:35.550 --> 35:37.880
the single-needle, double-thread kind.

35:37.880 --> 35:38.730
Okay, I'll wait for your call.

35:38.730 --> 35:40.460
They're in a hurry to sell them.

35:41.110 --> 35:42.070
Okay, okay.

35:42.380 --> 35:43.230
Hurry up.

35:44.320 --> 35:45.380
Exactly 2 minutes.

35:45.500 --> 35:46.560
I saved more money.

35:46.730 --> 35:47.010
Wait.

35:47.010 --> 35:47.670
Wait, wait.

35:48.340 --> 35:49.590
Tell me what's going on.

35:49.590 --> 35:51.650
Not playing your saxophone anymore?

35:52.130 --> 35:53.130
Didn't you say

35:54.050 --> 35:57.230
men have to make money?

35:57.380 --> 35:59.310
So you've thought of Mr. Lucky now?

36:00.230 --> 36:01.710
What do you want to do?

36:02.780 --> 36:03.860
How about you work with me fir—

36:03.860 --> 36:04.360
I'm in.

36:06.510 --> 36:07.400
You don't even know what I've been doing

36:07.400 --> 36:08.200
and you're in?

36:08.650 --> 36:09.860
Aren't you gonna ask if it's safe?

36:09.860 --> 36:11.190
I have you.

36:11.380 --> 36:12.910
Why do I need to ask?

36:13.050 --> 36:14.650
I don't need to ask anything.

36:15.380 --> 36:16.250
What I do now

36:16.320 --> 36:17.520
is called brokering.

36:17.760 --> 36:18.730
There are people buying,

36:18.730 --> 36:19.460
and people selling.

36:19.460 --> 36:20.590
Where there are sellers, there are buyers.

36:20.590 --> 36:21.510
But between the two,

36:21.510 --> 36:22.670
they might not know each other.

36:22.670 --> 36:23.820
We step in the middle,

36:23.820 --> 36:24.810
pull strings,

36:24.840 --> 36:26.900
and earn the price difference
as a middleman.

36:26.900 --> 36:27.900
In ancient times,

36:28.360 --> 36:30.090
it was a very noble profession.

36:30.320 --> 36:31.210
It was called a matchmaker.

36:31.210 --> 36:32.360
The one with a mole here,

36:32.360 --> 36:33.890
playing matchmaker,

36:33.940 --> 36:35.050
introducing people to each other.

36:35.050 --> 36:36.340
What about modern times?

36:36.340 --> 36:37.630
See, you're not listening.

36:37.630 --> 36:38.360
Didn't I just say?

36:38.360 --> 36:39.710
It's brokering.

36:40.000 --> 36:40.840
It's about information gaps.

36:40.840 --> 36:41.170
I'm telling you,

36:41.170 --> 36:42.210
you gotta be hardworking

36:42.210 --> 36:42.960
and smart to do this.

36:42.960 --> 36:43.500
I can do that.

36:43.500 --> 36:44.960
Collect info everywhere,

36:45.090 --> 36:46.220
perk up your ears,

36:46.340 --> 36:47.480
and take in every word.

36:47.480 --> 36:48.710
You need to keep your eyes wide open.

36:48.710 --> 36:49.800
Every strand of your hair must stand up

36:49.800 --> 36:50.800
like an antenna,

36:50.820 --> 36:52.880
collecting all money-making news.

36:52.960 --> 36:54.460
As long as I can drive a Benz,

36:54.460 --> 36:55.150
you can stick

36:55.150 --> 36:56.610
antennas all over my head.

36:56.760 --> 36:57.630
You wish.

36:57.690 --> 36:58.460
A Benz?

36:58.530 --> 37:00.060
Do you see me driving a Benz?

37:01.730 --> 37:02.440
You should pray first.

37:02.440 --> 37:03.670
Do you know how to pray?

37:03.670 --> 37:04.320
Let me teach you how.

37:04.280 --> 37:12.990
[Honesty and Mutual Success]

37:04.320 --> 37:05.340
There's a standard process for doing this.

37:05.340 --> 37:05.820
Kneel.

37:07.210 --> 37:07.730
That's why I say

37:07.730 --> 37:08.790
you're a lucky guy.

37:08.940 --> 37:10.110
There happens to be
a Hong Kong businessman recently

37:10.110 --> 37:11.460
looking to acquire a mainland factory.

37:11.460 --> 37:12.540
We hit the jackpot.

37:15.500 --> 37:16.070
Ma.

37:17.070 --> 37:19.020
To be honest with you,

37:19.550 --> 37:20.860
this private factory

37:20.940 --> 37:22.370
is my lifeblood.

37:23.610 --> 37:25.890
If it weren't for the severe losses,

37:27.320 --> 37:28.480
I really don't want to

37:28.480 --> 37:29.800
sell it.

37:31.730 --> 37:32.730
Director, you...

37:34.090 --> 37:35.690
Are you going to regret this?

37:36.280 --> 37:37.420
It's such a big factory,

37:37.420 --> 37:39.680
and it has been running for so many years.

37:40.010 --> 37:42.010
You really need to think it through.

37:42.070 --> 37:42.880
Yeah.

37:42.980 --> 37:44.880
What's there to think about?

37:45.340 --> 37:46.570
I've already arranged everything.

37:46.570 --> 37:47.460
That Hong Kong businessman

37:47.460 --> 37:50.060
will fly over with the money
in a couple of days.

37:52.460 --> 37:54.320
I hate to sell it, but what can I do?

37:55.000 --> 37:56.320
Everyone in the factory

37:56.320 --> 37:57.720
is waiting to be fed.

37:58.090 --> 37:59.290
If I don't sell it now,

38:00.300 --> 38:01.700
we really won't survive.

38:02.820 --> 38:05.550
Director, you really understand
the situation.

38:09.760 --> 38:11.170
Come on, move forward.

38:11.460 --> 38:12.740
Come.

38:12.920 --> 38:14.070
Move forward.

38:14.230 --> 38:16.650
Okay, stop. Alright.

38:18.650 --> 38:20.000
Mr. Huang, it must have been a long trip.

38:20.000 --> 38:20.910
Not at all.

38:21.070 --> 38:22.460
As long as there's money to be made,

38:22.460 --> 38:23.880
any hard work is worth it.

38:24.590 --> 38:25.610
Yes, yes.

38:25.650 --> 38:25.960
Right?

38:25.960 --> 38:27.010
Since we're doing business together,

38:27.010 --> 38:28.550
we are family, right?

38:30.760 --> 38:31.460
I'm sorry.

38:31.490 --> 38:33.120
I'm a clean freak.

38:33.340 --> 38:34.600
I understand.

38:35.500 --> 38:36.550
Businessmen probably

38:36.550 --> 38:38.250
all have their own quirks, right?

38:38.250 --> 38:39.580
That factory director—

38:39.730 --> 38:40.760
will he be difficult to deal with?

38:40.760 --> 38:42.440
Do we need to bribe him?

38:42.980 --> 38:44.350
We don't need to see him today,

38:44.350 --> 38:45.110
and no need for bribes either.

38:45.110 --> 38:45.760
For these little things,

38:45.760 --> 38:46.960
just leave them to me.

38:47.380 --> 38:48.380
Now that you're here,

38:48.380 --> 38:50.260
just eat well, drink well,

38:50.340 --> 38:52.140
and make yourself comfortable.

38:52.890 --> 38:54.490
What do you want to eat today?

38:54.920 --> 38:56.980
I heard Beijing has a lot of good food.

38:57.460 --> 38:58.550
There's plenty.

38:58.800 --> 38:59.380
Sir,

38:59.530 --> 39:00.670
park the car in that parking lot.

39:00.670 --> 39:02.000
We'll leave after eating.

39:02.000 --> 39:03.570
I'll take him to the hotel later.

39:03.570 --> 39:04.460
Let's go.

39:05.370 --> 39:07.770
[Wenzhou City Central Hospital]

39:08.010 --> 39:08.800
Dr. Zhang,

39:09.070 --> 39:10.780
I am Zhuang Meiqin's husband.

39:11.050 --> 39:12.710
I know you. Please take a seat.

39:16.460 --> 39:17.860
The test results are out.

39:18.110 --> 39:18.640
[Test Report]

39:18.660 --> 39:19.430
[CT Scan Report]

39:20.130 --> 39:21.130
It's lung cancer.

39:23.630 --> 39:25.150
The results came out a bit late.

39:25.150 --> 39:27.300
It is already in the middle
to late stages.

39:27.300 --> 39:28.880
But fortunately, the cancerous area

39:28.880 --> 39:29.810
isn't too large.

39:31.150 --> 39:31.920
The most important thing now

39:31.920 --> 39:34.320
is to arrange a surgery
as soon as possible.

39:34.500 --> 39:35.510
I'll have her do
some preoperative preparations

39:35.510 --> 39:36.820
over the next few days,

39:38.050 --> 39:40.180
and then we will schedule the surgery.

39:40.630 --> 39:41.900
Will she be okay?

39:43.900 --> 39:45.430
We can't be sure about that,

39:46.670 --> 39:48.030
but we will do our best.

39:51.900 --> 39:53.240
[Test Report]

39:53.270 --> 39:55.280
[They are consistent with the features
of peripherally-located lung cancer.]

40:07.650 --> 40:09.990
[Seasons Change Hostel]

40:10.020 --> 40:15.330
[Receipt from
Peking Union Medical College Hospital]

40:30.100 --> 40:31.630
Why are you looking at this?

40:32.670 --> 40:36.730
You lied to me.

40:40.050 --> 40:43.380
I didn't lie to you.

40:44.010 --> 40:45.550
This is so expensive.

40:46.650 --> 40:47.670
What?

40:50.190 --> 40:53.780
Where did you get the money?
You borrowed it?

40:57.590 --> 40:59.250
Where did the money come from?

41:05.650 --> 41:09.590
We have to thank Ranran

41:10.590 --> 41:14.690
for making this surgery possible.

41:17.050 --> 41:17.880
Ranran?

41:19.980 --> 41:21.130
I can...

41:21.760 --> 41:24.960
pay this money back.

41:26.110 --> 41:28.530
Trust me.

41:29.170 --> 41:30.840
We'll pay it back together.

41:33.440 --> 41:36.420
You've suffered a lot.

41:36.630 --> 41:37.550
It's nothing.

41:47.730 --> 41:48.390
Gentlemen.

41:48.840 --> 41:50.000
Today we are formally holding

41:50.000 --> 41:51.130
a negotiation meeting

41:51.130 --> 41:53.970
on foreign investment partnership.

41:52.120 --> 42:00.490
[Negotiation Meeting
on Foreign Investment Partnership]

41:54.460 --> 41:55.410
This meeting

41:55.440 --> 41:56.190
is based on

41:56.530 --> 41:58.660
principles of openness and equality,

41:59.000 --> 42:01.350
aimed at addressing
the difficulties of our factory.

42:01.350 --> 42:02.440
We've invited Mr. Huang,

42:02.440 --> 42:04.060
who came all the way

42:04.110 --> 42:04.970
from Hong Kong,

42:05.000 --> 42:05.530
as well as

42:05.570 --> 42:06.970
Mr. Zhu and Mr. Li,

42:07.090 --> 42:08.950
who are interested in investing.

42:09.190 --> 42:10.970
Everyone is encouraged

42:11.190 --> 42:12.450
to be honest, sincere,

42:17.550 --> 42:18.630
and speak freely.

42:23.150 --> 42:23.790
We are

42:23.960 --> 42:25.290
all doing big business.

42:25.530 --> 42:28.160
What matters is investment versus return.

42:28.400 --> 42:30.340
Spending a little money
to make a big profit—

42:30.340 --> 42:31.400
that's a good deal.

42:32.280 --> 42:32.780
We think

42:32.820 --> 42:34.570
the current purchase price

42:34.800 --> 42:35.740
is reasonable,

42:36.010 --> 42:38.150
and the factory's performance is stable,

42:38.150 --> 42:39.480
so we're willing to bid.

42:42.880 --> 42:43.610
Director.

42:44.710 --> 42:47.420
I've actually inspected

42:47.530 --> 42:50.220
many similar-sized companies

42:50.530 --> 42:52.280
in the mainland.

42:53.900 --> 42:55.520
Your price today

42:55.710 --> 42:56.710
is not low.
